learn the truth about Verheek's death.  

807
01:14:45,760 --> 01:14:47,600
Lewis brought the news to his office.

808
01:14:49,040 --> 01:14:53,440
'Denton, when are we going to start 
taking this Pelican Brief seriously?'  

809
01:14:54,080 --> 01:15:00,800
he asked. 'People keep dying because of it. We'd 
better investigate it. It must be Mattiece.'

